{
 "file": "_STG18B.bin",
 "source_size": 44228,
 "built_size": 47234,
 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1618",
   "jp_len": 153,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "{00}ゃ{00}か{00}ィ{00}げ{00}ッ{00}わ{00}分{00}オ{00}招？{00}D{00}I{00}に{00}。{00}…{00}ぞ{00}ル{00}そ{00}ュ{00}ウ{00}連{00}ロ{00}{01}{01}ク{00}{01}{01}Sぁあいうえおかダチッツテ{01}デ、トドナ。つネハバパ·々ビブベミメちっぞャー（ルでど縛ぬ縛回艦気球るカね君·{00}！撃{01}M開アな、{00}{01}！思{00}Mぬんな、{00}{01}ぁ叛逆者拉克丝·克莱因！停止抵抗、乖乖{00}投降！",
   "zh_hex": ""
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16d6",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "前后夹击吗……这下可真叫人伤脑筋啊",
   "zh_hex": "15bae7feec5be7cce8020909e7b989e7c4e820e8c1b4e8f9eb67ef56e7c30000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x170a",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请开放全频段通信",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae7fae86cefb4eec6ea6bef59e90f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x173b",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……拉克丝！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c2e7d5e8a3ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1770",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是拉克丝·克莱因",
   "zh_hex": "158be7b6e7c2e7d5e8a304e7d5e846ef3300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x177c",
   "jp_len": 41,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正因为各自期盼的未来不同、我们才不得{00}不与萨拉议长走向敌对、",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3bef33e7c1e819efb5eac9ecf3e7b4e8b4efcfe7b5e85d02efcce7bbe836e7b5e80a00e7b5e832e83be7c2e8e3ef34e890efc1e7e3e7be020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17a5",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我不愿与你们交战",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b5e961e832e7b8e7bbe861ef280000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17b8",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "还请放这艘船过去吧、然后、也请各位再{00}一次……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f7e83ae86ce7b9eb18ea02ef36e7ebe7d002e7efe7fe02e7c0e83ae819e834e80b00efb6e86409090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17d3",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请大家好好想一想、我们真正非战不可的{00}对象、究竟是什么",
   "zh_hex": "15e83aefa5e7dfe7c7e7c7e7e6efb6e7e602efcce7bbe820ef3be8f0ef28e7b5e7c4e7b400e7beebf202e906ef2ce7b6e7dde7bd0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x181b",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "队长……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c9ef340909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1848",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1880",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不行！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5efd6ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18b0",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18d6",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "绝不能放那艘舰逃过去！",
   "zh_hex": "15e91ce7b5e7c6e86ce7b7eb18e7d4e8c2ef36e7ebef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18e8",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那艘舰上、可搭载着配备N干扰消除器的{00}MS！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7eb18e7d4ef4c02e7c4eb09eb1de86dea34e877eed3e8d3ebc7e928e974e8c3e7b400efa7ef9eef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1929",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "N干扰消除器！？",
   "zh_hex": "15eed3e8d3ebc7e928e974e8c3ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1953",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么可能！拉克丝大人{00}可是被誉为PLANT歌姬的人物啊！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde7c4e7c606e7c2e7d5e8a3beb400e7c4e7b6e7f1ed05e7c1eed4e024ea9ceed3eed6efd0ed56e7b4b4e99ee7c30605000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1971",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那位大人、怎么会做出背叛我们这种事来{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e834efa5efb202e7f2e7bde7e2e81cefbee9e4ef43efcce7bbe7b9e7d1efb8efcf0009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19ab",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可蕾蒂·安大人、可是打心底里盼着与{00}PLANT和谈的啊！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e84ce9f504e7fcbeb402e7c4e7b6e7f5e82de9b4ef31ecf3e86de83200eed4e024ea9ceed3eed6e7d3eaf4e7b4e7c306050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19cd",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我实在无法想象、那位大人竟会说谎！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce87fef29e7dce84ee7e6ebf202e7b7e834efa5efb2ef2ce7e2e7edec96ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a0b",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那东西若是落入蓝色宇宙之手、",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e8bae7f8e7e7e7b6e92ae891eaf1e89fe8bee8bfe7cdae02000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a1e",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "地球与PLANT之间、过去的悲剧{00}恐怕将会再度重演",
   "zh_hex": "15bf95e832eed4e024ea9ceed3eed6e7cde8fc02ef36e7ebe7b4e9dfecb500eb33e958e84ae7e2e80be96de8a1ea2f000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a3c",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "若各位真心渴望和平、那么那艘舰就绝不{00}该存在于世！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e7e819e834e820e82ded84e965e7d3e88702e7b7e7bde7b7eb18e7d4e7c5e91ce7b500e898e993ef29e879e83cef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a84",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……她还真有一手、那样一来、我们就彻{00}底成了坏人了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e88ee7f7e820e7cbefb6ef6602e7b7e7daefb6efcf02efcce7bbe7c5ebc500e9b4e837e7bae9edefb2e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a9f",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、我们该怎么办？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02efcce7bbe898e7f2e7bde8ea050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ac4",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……突破吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8b6c7e7d000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ad0",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "因为我们、是绝不能在这里停下脚步的",
   "zh_hex": "15ef33e7c1efcce7bb02e7b6e91ce7b5e7c6ef29e7b9ef31e934ef4deb68ea93e7b40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b01",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唉……只能上了",
   "zh_hex": "15ea5d0909ef32e7c6ef4ce7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b33",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我也上！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7c0ef4cef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b63",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请尽量避开驾驶舱、阿斯兰",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae8f2e851cae7fae953e975ebeb02e7d2e7c8e86f000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b96",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我尽力",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce8f2efb00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bc6",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "难道是我太鲁莽了吗……",
   "zh_hex": "15e866e82ae7b68be86ae8a2edb2e7bae8020909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c07",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿斯兰！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e7c8e86fef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c30",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "基拉！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e829e7c2ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c5c",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哟、少年！你是来救我们的吗！！",
   "zh_hex": "15eb2c02eface909ef97e7b8e7b6efcfe8caefcce7bbe7b4e802ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c92",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "巴尔特菲尔德……先生？",
   "zh_hex": "15e85be7e1e7cfea6ce7e1e82c0909ef8bef8d050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cc3",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这里是大天使号、我是玛琉·拉米亚斯！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9ef31e7b6efa5e844e83fe83302efcce7b6e845ead2ef4be7c2e878e7d6e7c8ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cd6",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您是拉克丝·克莱因吧？{00}我们是来救援的！",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7b6e7c2e7d5e8a304e7d5e846ef33e7d005008be7bbe7b6d9e8cae863e7b406000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d0f",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这里是永恒号、我是拉克丝·克莱因",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9ef31e7b6e9bfeb85e833028be7b6e7c2e7d5e8a304e7d5e846ef3300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d1f",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "感谢救援",
   "zh_hex": "15e87de8b2e8cae8630000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d47",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们这边正被一群MS团团围住、陷入了{00}苦战！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe7b9e899ef3be7f1efb6ecfaefa7ef9eea5eea5ee9dee85902eaf9e891e7ba00e9e6ef28ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d61",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要是能帮我们突破这重包围、那就帮大忙{00}了！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae7b6e7c6e910efcce7bbe8b6ef6de7b9e8a1eabbe9de02e7b7e7c5e910efa5ea0600e7baef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d9b",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "明白",
   "zh_hex": "15ef39e8090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1dad",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "MS队立即出击！前去救援永恒号！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efa7ef9ee7c9e86be855efbee7ccef97ef51e7ebe8cae863e9bfeb85e833ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ded",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不妙啊……再这样下去、就要让他们给逃{00}掉了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ecc7e7c30909e80be7b9e7daef4de7eb02e7c5ef2ae7f9e80ce7bbe839e8c200e9d3e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e2c",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我吗？",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e4f",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正是、蕾蒂·安大佐",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3be7b602e84ce9f5ef4be7fcefa5efba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e5e",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "若您能在此亲自出击、扎夫特对您的信任{00}也会随之提升",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e7e835e7c6ef29e7cae894efb5efbee7cc02e84be830e7cfe7bee835e7b4e90fe89a00e7c0e7e2e9a1e7cde821ed2b0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e99",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可我……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4efcc09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ebe",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这可是个难得的机会、大佐",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7c4e7b6e828e866e80ae7b4e7e4e7e202efa5efba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ecd",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要打倒阿兹拉埃尔、救出特列斯阁下、就{00}只剩这条路了……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae7f5e848e7d2e856e7c2e96ae7e102e8caefbee7cfe8b5e7c8e8d7ef4d02e7c500ef32ea3ae7b9e9d4e8d2e7ba09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f07",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "特列斯大人他……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cfe8b5e7c8efa5efb2e80c09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f28",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我明白了",
   "zh_hex": "150909efccef39e809e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f4a",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请您看着我吧、特列斯大人",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae835e7f6e86defcce7d002e7cfe8b5e7c8efa5efb20000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f59",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我一定会……",
   "zh_hex": "15efccefb6e867e7e209090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f87",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c30909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f98",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、我是……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc02efcce7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fd0",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哎呀哎呀……总算是得救了、大天使号的{00}各位",
   "zh_hex": "15e9dce9c6e9dce9c60909e881e889e7b6e80ae8cae7ba02efa5e844e83fe833e7b400e819e8340000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2001",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我再次向各位致谢",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce80be864efc1e819e834ea32e8b20000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x202f",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "追击而来的那些MS、看样子不会再出现{00}了",
   "zh_hex": "15e8dde7cce89cefcfe7b4e7b7e8a4efa7ef9e02e7f6e7dae886e7b5e7e2e80befbee82f00e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2046",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "趁现在、赶紧离开这里……",
   "zh_hex": "15e9eae82fef2902ea04eaede901e7fae7b9ef3109090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2096",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "3点方向、确认到新的敌影！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef60e822efb1efc102e88ce8a0e7d7ef8ae7b4e7e3ea8eef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20c2",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……有敌人！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7cbe7e3efb2ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20f0",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那台MS……是OZ吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7ea16efa7ef9e0909e7b6ed1ceedae802ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x211f",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b509090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x214b",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那是艾比安高达",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7b6e8d6e825e7fce812ef2b0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x215a",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "杰克斯·马吉斯……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ebe7d5e7c804e84fe7d9e7c809090600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x218a",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那可不对、希罗·尤尔",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c4e7b5e7be02e87be7ecef4bea5fe7e10000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21b5",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……什么？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7dde7bd050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21d8",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那位大人是米利亚尔特·匹斯克拉福特、{00}我们白色獠牙的领导者……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e834beb4e7b6e878e82ee7d6e7e1e7cf04ed2ae7c8e7d5e7c2ea7ce7cf02008be7bbe809e89fececebd7e7b4ea20ea4bad090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x221b",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "杰克斯、你这家伙……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ebe7d5e7c802e7b8e7b9e7dfe7fd0909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x224a",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "如今我该交谈的对象、并不是你",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f0efb9efcce898e861eaf4e7b4e7beebf202e957e7b5e7b6e7b80000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2282",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "PLANT议长帕特里克·萨拉！{00}听得见吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15eed4e024ea9ceed3eed6e8e3ef34eb01e7cfef31e7d504e83be7c20600e8d1e80ae85ce8020605000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2296",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我乃白色獠牙的领导者、米利亚尔特·匹{00}斯克拉福特！",
   "zh_hex": "158befdde809e89fececebd7e7b4ea20ea4bad02e878e82ee7d6e7e1e7cf04ed2a00e7c8e7d5e7c2ea7ce7cf06000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22d5",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你说米利亚尔特·匹斯克拉福特？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7ede878e82ee7d6e7e1e7cf04ed2ae7c8e7d5e7c2ea7ce7cf05000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22e4",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你一个地球王室的人、找我们这些调整者{00}究竟有何贵干！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8efb6e828ef63efd3e884ec62e7b4efb202e9d2efcce7bbe7b9e8a4e95ce9feef6e00e906ef2ce7cbefbce930e8d3ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x231a",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "作为同样以地球为敌的一方、我们希望能{00}与你们扎夫特携手共斗！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2fe7c1e85de7dae7f3ef63efd3e7c1e7e3e7b4efb6efb102efcce7bbe87be965e7c600e832e7b8e7bbe84be830e7cfec1def66ea48e7ffef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2359",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x238f",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "杰克斯……你这家伙！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ebe7d5e7c80909e7b8e7b9e7dfe7fdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23b5",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "杰克斯……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ebe7d5e7c80909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23e9",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这家伙、又来了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7dfe7fd02e8f1efcfe7ba09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2443",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要和、和我们共斗！？你一个自然人、究{00}竟为何……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae7d302e7d3efcce7bbea48e7ffef9705e7b8efb6e828efb5e7efefb202e90600ef2ce7c1efbc09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2477",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……你是信不过我吗？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b8e7b6e90fe7b5ef36efcce802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2483",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那就只能用我们的行动来证明！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c5ef32e7c6efb3efcce7bbe7b4efd6ef30efcfeba3ef39ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24ba",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "白色獠牙的MS部队！正朝我们这边逼近{00}过来！",
   "zh_hex": "15e809e89fececebd7e7b41314cce7c906ef3beaad8be7bbe7b9e899ebf69600ef36d90600000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24ef",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……拉米亚斯舰长！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c2e878e7d6e7c8e7d4ef34ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x251a",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是啊{00}看样子、我们也只能应战了……",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e7c300e7f6e7dae886028be7bbe7c0ef32e7c6e873ef28e7ba090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2556",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "杰克斯·马吉斯……你这家伙、到底在打{00}什么主意？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ebe7d5e7c804e84fe7d9e7c80909e7b8e7b9e7dfe7fd02e7d7e9b4ef29e7f500e7dde7bde954ef3c05000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2589",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就如我方才所说的那样、希罗·尤尔",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7f0efccefb1e836e7fbe7ede7b4e7b7e7da02e87be7ecef4bea5fe7e10000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x259c",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们的目的、是排除一切与殖民地为敌的{00}存在……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe7b4efd4e7b402e7b6ea67e974efb6ef3fe832e8a9ef38ef63e7c1e7e3e7b400e993ef2909090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25b3",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "也就是说、地球本身就是我们的敌人！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c0e7c5e7b6e7ed02ef63efd3efa6e88de7c5e7b6efcce7bbe7b4e7e3efb2ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25dc",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7dde7bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2600",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "凡是会妨碍这一目的的、不论是谁、都唯{00}有将其排除！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ec0ce7b6e7e2e97fe8c6e7b9efb6efd4e7b4e7b402e7b5e8dce7b6e92302e840ea8900e7cbe84ae8cfea67e974ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2620",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "上吧、希罗！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef4ce7d002e87be7ecef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2650",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "杰克斯！这到底是怎么回事……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ebe7d5e7c8ef97e7b9e7d7e9b4e7b6e7f2e7bdef52efb80909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2662",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您究竟打算要做什么？",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e906ef2ce7f5e889ef2ae81ce7dde7bd050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2697",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "无意向你解释",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dcef3cefc1e7b8e89dec9f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26ba",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……杰克斯！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8ebe7d5e7c8ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26e3",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "让开、诺茵！哪怕是你、只要敢妨碍我、{00}我也照打不误！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f9e7fa02e972e971ef97e8ffe958e7b6e7b802ef32ef2ae8cde97fe8c6efcc0200efcce7c0ea1ae7f5e7b5ea33ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2715",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "杰、杰克斯……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8eb02e8ebe7d5e7c80909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2745",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "住手！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e859ae0606000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x274f",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们只不过、是想从这里离开罢了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbef32e7b5ef3602e7b6e7e6e88ae7b9ef31e901e7faeaefe7baef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2784",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……离开了又能怎样？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e901e7fae7bae8f1e7c6e7f2e7da050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27ad",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bd050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27d0",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "把拉克丝·克莱因带出PLANT之后、{00}你们打算怎么办？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81be7c2e7d5e8a304e7d5e846ef33e937afeed4e024ea9ceed3eed6e7cde7fe0200e7b8e7bbe7f5e889e7f2e7bde8ea050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27ef",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "光是她的存在本身、就会给这世界播下争{00}端的火种！",
   "zh_hex": "15e83de7b6e88ee7b4e993ef29efa6e88d02e7c5e7e2e839e7b9e83ce8f5ed70ef4de85200eab1e7b4e8dae7d1ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2810",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、在那之前于此地把你们讨灭、便是{00}对世界而言的必然！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02ef29e7b7e7cdef51e879e7caef63e81be7b8e7bbe9f7e8e102e8fae7b600e7bee83ce8f5e89cefd7e7b4e860e7efef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2851",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你这家伙……竟想对拉克丝下手！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b9e7dfe7fd0909ef2ce7e6e7bee7c2e7d5e8a3ef4def66ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x285d",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那种事、我绝不会让你得逞！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7d1efb802efcce91ce7b5e7e2e7f9e7b8e80ae9ebef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2892",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "身为匹斯克拉福特王室一员的您、为何要{00}站到扎夫特那一边？",
   "zh_hex": "15e88de7c1ed2ae7c8e7d5e7c2ea7ce7cfe884ec62efb6e849e7b4e83502e7c1efbcef2a00ec31e7d7e84be830e7cfe7b7efb6e899050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28cd",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "因为他们是与地球为敌之人！作为协力的{00}理由、这就足够了",
   "zh_hex": "15ef33e7c1e80ce7bbe7b6e832ef63efd3e7c1e7e3e7cdefb2ef97ef2fe7c1e8f6efb0e7b400e872e8a602e7b9e7c5ea1ee920e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2909",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您是打算把地球本身{00}整个都毁灭掉吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7b6e7f5e889e81bbf95d2e88d00e9fee828e840e97ce8e1e9d3e802050000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x291f",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "将其毁灭之后、您又打算做什么呢？",
   "zh_hex": "15e84ae8cfe97ce8e1e7cde7fe02e835e8f1e7f5e889e81ce7dde7bde907050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x294e",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要作为争端元凶的地球消失、就再没有{00}什么非做不可的了……！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2aef2fe7c1e852eab1ecaeecb2e7b4ef63efd3e928e8a502e7c5e80be7d8e7cb00e7dde7bde8f0e81ce7b5e7c4e7b4e7ba0909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2971",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "如今我们该做的、绝不是去选择和谈这种{00}半途折中的办法！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f0efb9efcce7bbe898e81ce7b402e91ce7b5e7b6e7ebe966eaaae7d3eaf4e7b9e7d100eadeebf5ed64ef4ee7b4e8eae84eef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2997",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唯有从根本上加以纠正的行动、才是真正{00}必要的！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea89e7cbe88ae9b8efa6ef4ce854e7f3eda2ef3be7b4efd6ef3002e836e7b6e820ef3b00e860ef2ae7b4ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29c7",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您……",
   "zh_hex": "15e83509090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29ea",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你这种追求和谈的行为、对我们白色獠牙{00}来说、就是一种障碍……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b9e7d1e8dde93ae7d3eaf4e7b49fe7c102e7be8be7bbe809e89fececebd700d9e7ed02e7c5e7b687e7d1ebfce8c60909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a0b",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我对你并无仇恨、但请你在此消失吧！拉{00}克丝·克莱因！",
   "zh_hex": "158be7bee7b8e957e7dceaa3e9be02e7dbe83ae7b8ef29e7cae928e8a5e7d006e7c200e7d5e8a304e7d5e846ef3306000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a4d",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "米利亚尔特·匹斯克拉福特……",
   "zh_hex": "15e878e82ee7d6e7e1e7cf04ed2ae7c8e7d5e7c2ea7ce7cf0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a5b",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "舍弃了杰克斯·马吉斯这副假面、你得出{00}的结论、就是这个吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15eb17e938e7bae8ebe7d5e7c804e84fe7d9e7c8e7b9ecb6eb28e86202e7b8e80aaf00e7b4e868e8dc02e7c5e7b6e7b9e828e8020500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a94",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你应该能明白……那些压迫宇宙之民的地{00}球人、是何等愚蠢",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e873e898e7c6ef39e8090909e7b7e8a4e992eb70e8bee8bfe7cdef38e7b4ef6300efd3efb202e7b6efbce826e959e94b0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ab8",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、就是要纠正这一切！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc02e7c5e7b6ef2aeda2ef3be7b9efb6ef3fef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ae1",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "荒唐！",
   "zh_hex": "15ec38edf7ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ae8",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那不就和当年的扎比家、还有OZ想做的{00}事毫无二致了吗！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b5e7c5e7d3c4e909e7b4e84be825e7df02e7f7e7cbed1ceedae7e6e81ce7b400a9ea0ae7dcea13ea32e7bae802060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b27",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "如今已不是讲究手段的时候了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f0efb9ef3ae7b5e7b6eba2e906ef66ea6be7b4ef2dea39e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b3b",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "地球已经到了那种地步……不、是整个世{00}界都已被逼到了绝境",
   "zh_hex": "15ef63efd3ef3ae8b7e7d7e7bae7b7e7d1ef63ea930909e7b502e7b6e9fee828e83c00e8f5e840ef3ae7f1ebf6e7d7e7bae91ceb810000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b56",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你其实也早该察觉到了吧！？夏亚·阿兹{00}纳布尔！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e8cfe87fe7c0e963e898ea8be8aee7d7e7bae7d0ef9705ef37e7d6ef4be7d2e85600e882e831e7e1ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b8c",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……可即便如此、我也绝对无法认同你正{00}想去做的这件事",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c4e855e8fae7f0e7ca02efcce7c0e91ce7bee7dce84ee8a0e85de7b8ef3b00e7e6e7ebe81ce7b4e7b9e991efb80000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2bcc",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……你要与我为敌也无妨、不过你给我记{00}住、夏亚·阿兹纳布尔",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b8ef2ae832efcce7c1e7e3e7c0e7dce97f02e7b5ef36e7b8e839efcce99600e85902ef37e7d6ef4be7d2e856e882e831e7e10000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2bef",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "总有一天、你也终将承认、我现在的这一{00}行为是正确的！",
   "zh_hex": "15e881e7cbefb6e84402e7b8e7c0e8e2e84aea75e8a002efcce82fef29e7b4e7b9efb600efd6e7c1e7b6ef3be88ce7b4ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c41",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、竟会认同他的所作所为……？",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc02ef2ce7e2e8a0e85de80ce7b4e7fbef2fe7fbe7c10909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c76",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您怎么了！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7f2e7bde7baef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ca1",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这下可有点不妙了啊、主引擎它……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9ef4de7c4e7cbe822e7b5ecc7e7bae7c302e954e9d0ec1ee97809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2cdc",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正是良机！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3be7b6eaf0e7e4ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ce2",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "拿下你了、拉克丝·克莱因！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9a789e7b8e7ba02e7c2e7d5e8a304e7d5e846ef33060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d16",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……杰克斯！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8ebe7d5e7c8ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d43",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请住手、杰克斯！",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae859ef6602e8ebe7d5e7c8ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d7f",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么、是诺茵！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bd02e7b6e972e971ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d96",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！快让开、诺茵！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7deef97e85fe7f9e7fa02e972e971ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2dcd",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不！我绝不让开！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef97efcce91ce7b5e7f9e7faef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e00",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "别碍事！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e5e8c6efb8ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e16",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你要是再不肯让开、我连你也一并当成障{00}碍排除掉！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8ef2ae7b6e80be7b5e93de7f9e7fa028be86ee7b8e7c087e957c4e837ebfc00e8c6ea67e974e9d306000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e62",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就算是那样、我也无所谓……杰克斯",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e889e7b6e7b7e7da02efcce7c0e7dce7fbe92b0909e8ebe7d5e7c80000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e98",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "诺茵！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e972e971ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ec4",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、在那之前、请先告诉我！您到底为{00}什么、要做这种事！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602ef29e7b7e7cdef5102e83aef8be8e5ead6efccef97e835e7d7e9b4e7c100e7dde7bd02ef2ae81ce7b9e7d1efb8ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2eec",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "身为匹斯克拉福特王室一员的您、竟亲手{00}去做这散播纷争的勾当……",
   "zh_hex": "15e88de7c1ed2ae7c8e7d5e7c2ea7ce7cfe884ec62efb6e849e7b4e83502ef2ce894ef6600e7ebe81ce7b9ef68ed70ecf8e852e7b4ecb7ef5309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f19",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您可曾想过、莉莉娜大人会为此有多么伤{00}心难过吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7c4ea2ae7e6ef3602e81ee81ee7eaefa5efb2e7e2e7c1e7cae7cbe7e9e7bde8f900e82de866ef36e802ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f8d",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……杰克斯！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8ebe7d5e7c8ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2fc5",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我没什么好对你说的！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7d8e7dde7bde7c7e7bee7b8e7ede7b4ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3004",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……杰克斯！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8ebe7d5e7c8ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x303c",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "杰克斯、您到底是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ebe7d5e7c802e835e7d7e9b4e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x307f",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（原谅我吧、诺茵……）",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8ee8e4ec95efcce7d002e972e9710909ef8f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x30b1",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x30eb",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……最后问一句",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8c5e7fee997efb6ebb90000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x30fa",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "杰克斯·马吉斯、{00}你这番话、是当真的吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ebe7d5e7c804e84fe7d9e7c80200e7b8e7b9ee6de81f02e7b6c4e820e7b4e8020500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3129",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "事到如今、你还问什么……！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb8e7d7e7f0efb902e7b8e7f7e997e7dde7bd0909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3134",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我正是为了真正与地球为敌、才站到这里{00}来的",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef3be7b6e7c1e7bae820ef3be832ef63efd3e7c1e7e302e836ec31e7d7e7b9ef3100efcfe7b40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3169",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哪怕那会散播出新的战乱、您也在所不惜{00}吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ffe958e7b7e7e2ef68ed70efbeef8ae7b4ef28e97602e835e7c0ef29e7fbe7b5e9c800e802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x31a2",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这一切、我心里全都一清二楚！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b987ef3f028be82def31bbe84087e995ea13ebd306060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x31c9",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那就是你的真意吗",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7c5e7b6e7b8e7b4e820ef3ce8020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x31d7",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、杰克斯·马吉斯……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e8ebe7d5e7c804e84fe7d9e7c80909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x320e",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我要杀了你！",
   "zh_hex": "150909efccef2ae89be7bae7b8ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3243",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不行！我怎能就这样死在你的手上！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5efd6ef97efcce7f2e7c6e7c5e7b9e7daef6aef29e7b8e7b4ef66ef4cef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3281",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……杰克斯！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8ebe7d5e7c8ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x32b9",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "太慢了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e86ae979e7ba06060000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x32f3",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3305",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这种动作……难道是零式系统！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7d1ef30ef2f0909e866e82ae7b6eb74ea26e941e9290605000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x333a",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7beef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x334b",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我已经将零式系统的力量、化为了我自己{00}的、希罗·尤尔！",
   "zh_hex": "158bef3ae8b7e84aeb74ea26e941e929e7b4dae85102e9a5e7c1e7ba8babe8c900e7b402e87be7ec04ea5fe7e1060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3398",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "杰克斯！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ebe7d5e7c8ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x33c5",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就连艾比安高达、也已经撑不下去了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e86ee8d6e825e7fce812ef2b02e7c0ef3ae8b7ea29e7b589e7ebe7ba0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x33d7",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这场胜负、就先寄存着、希罗·尤尔！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e876e8dbe92c02e7c5b8e803e993e86d02e87be7ec04ea5fe7e1060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x340d",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "杰克斯……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ebe7d5e7c809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3414",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "马吉斯……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e84fe7d9e7c8090906000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3441",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "到此为止了、杰克斯·马吉斯",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d7e7cae7c1e869e7ba02e8ebe7d5e7c804e84fe7d9e7c8000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3450",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你成不了地球之敌",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e837e7b5e7baef63efd3e7cde7e30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3464",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就在这里、由我们……亲手杀了你",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5ef29e7b9ef3102e8a6efcce7bb0909e894ef66e89be7bae7b80000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3491",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "很遗憾、那可由不得你！",
   "zh_hex": "15e981eba9ed6102e7b7e7c4e8a6e7b5e80ae7b8ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x34c6",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……杰克斯！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8ebe7d5e7c8ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x34f4",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这场胜负就先寄存着、大天使号！{00}还有你、希罗·尤尔！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e876e8dbe92ce7c5b8e803e993e86d02bee844e83fe8330600e7f7e7cbe7b802e87be7ec04ea5fe7e10600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3534",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "杰克斯、您到底是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ebe7d5e7c802e835e7d7e9b4e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x356d",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "敌部队的反应、已经全部消失了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e3ef70e7c9e7b4e87ce87302ef3ae8b7efb4ef70e928e8a5e7baef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x359a",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "拉米亚斯舰长！要撤的话、就趁现在！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c2e878e7d6e7c8e7d4ef34ef97ef2ae90ae7b4e81f02e7c5e9eae82fef29ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x35d5",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "MS队立即返回母舰！！我们这就脱离这{00}片宙域！",
   "zh_hex": "151314e7c9e86be855eba88ce9d5e7d406068be7bbe7b9e7c5e9e5e901e7b900ee5ee8bfeaa706000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3619",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3647",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……你醒了啊",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b8eb20e7bae7c3000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x36b7",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "！？你是……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef9705e7b8e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x36de",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "特列斯让我去救你",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cfe8b5e7c8e7f9efcce7ebe8cae7b80000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3710",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "特列斯……大人他？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cfe8b5e7c80909efa5efb2e80c050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3737",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "蕾蒂·安……你真正该待的地方、并不在{00}这宇宙",
   "zh_hex": "15e84ce9f5ef4be7fc0909e7b8e820ef3be898eaa8e7b4ef63efb102e957e7b5ef2900e7b9e8bee8bf0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3753",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "回到那位身边吧",
   "zh_hex": "15ef52e7d7e7b7e834e88de899e7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x377f",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "特列斯大人他？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cfe8b5e7c8efa5efb2e80c050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x37a3",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他可不是那种、会一直栽在阿兹拉埃尔那{00}种货色手里的人",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7c4e7b5e7b6e7b7e7d102e7e287e875ec5def29e7d2e856e7c2e96ae7e1e7b700e7d1eaf5e89faeef31e7b4b40000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x37c4",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "用不了多久、他就会重新回到台前",
   "zh_hex": "15efb3e7b5e7bae7e9e9db02e80ce7c5e7e2e8a1ef8aef52e7d7ea16ef510000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x37f8",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是吗……特列斯大人他……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e8020909e7cfe8b5e7c8efa5efb2e80c09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3834",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我得向你道谢、杰克斯·马吉斯",
   "zh_hex": "1509098be80a9de7b8e82ae8b202e8ebe7d5e7c804e84fe7d9e7c80000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3869",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……从这里开始、就是我该做的事了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e88ae7b9ef31e7fae90802e7c5e7b6efcce898e81ce7b4efb8e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3894",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来……确实是这样",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcf0909e88ce87fe7b6e7b9e7da0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x38a0",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我们下次相见之时、就是在战场了、{00}杰克斯·马吉斯",
   "zh_hex": "1509098be7bb89e864e8b1e85ce7cdef2d02e7c5e7b6ef29ef28e876e7ba0200e8ebe7d5e7c804e84fe7d9e7c80000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x38d8",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯……战场见",
   "zh_hex": "15e8650909ef28e876e85c0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x38e6",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "以彼此为敌的身份相见",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f3efc9e7cae7c1e7e3e7b4e88dea22e8b1e85c0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3907",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我的名字、叫米利亚尔特·匹斯克拉福特",
   "zh_hex": "158be7b4e8ace98002e8c1e878e82ee7d6e7e1e7cf04ed2ae7c8e7d5e7c2ea7ce7cf00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3918",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "也是殖民地解放组织、白色獠牙的领导者",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c0e7b6e8a9ef38bfe89de86cea0deb3f02e809e89fececebd7e7b4ea20ea4bad00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x392f",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "地球与宇宙……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef63efd3e832e8bee8bf09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3939",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正是这两者的存在、催生出了对立的格局{00}……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3be7b6e7b9e97def6ee7b4e993ef2902ed22ef8defbee7bae7bee86be7b4e824ea8c000909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3955",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "因此、我们……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef33e7ca02efcce7bb09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3960",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在此宣告、我们将与扎夫特携手、排除掉{00}与宇宙对立的地球！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e7caeccce8e502efcce7bbe84ae832e84be830e7cfec1def6602ea67e974e9d300e832e8bee8bfe7bee86be7b4ef63efd3ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3999",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "白色獠牙……",
   "zh_hex": "15e809e89fececebd709090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x39be",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哎呀哎呀……一个棘手的家伙、竟成了扎{00}夫特的盟友啊",
   "zh_hex": "15e9dce9c6e9dce9c60909efb6e828ed79ef66e7b4e7dfe7fd02ef2ce837e7bae84b00e830e7cfe7b4ec7fe960e7c30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x39f6",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这一来、萨拉议长对地球的对抗姿态、只{00}会变得越发强硬了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9efb6efcf02e83be7c2e8e3ef34e7beef63efd3e7b4e7bee912ebbee99402ef3200e7e2e955e80aea57e870e8adeb97e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3a3f",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "父亲他……说要灭绝自然人……他确实是{00}这么说的",
   "zh_hex": "15e888e894e80c0909e7edef2ae8e1e91cefb5e7efefb20909e80ce88ce87fe7b600e7b9e7bde7ede7b40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3a74",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "OZ也不会罢休……",
   "zh_hex": "15ed1ceedae7c0e7b5e7e2eaefe90e09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3a87",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "蓝色宇宙的阿兹拉埃尔、也一定会采取某{00}种行动",
   "zh_hex": "15eaf1e89fe8bee8bfe7b4e7d2e856e7c2e96ae7e102e7c087e867e7e2ec9ee987eae800e7d19fef3000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3abe",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "扎夫特与OZ的全面对决……",
   "zh_hex": "15e84be830e7cfe832ed1ceedae7b4efb4e862e7bee8ab09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3ae8",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那也极有可能",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c0eacae7cbe7c4e7c60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3b13",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唯独这一点、无论如何都必须设法阻止才{00}行",
   "zh_hex": "15ea89e8eee7b9efb6e82202e7dce8dce7f0efbce840e860e9a2eb43e84ee8efe869e83600efd60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3b47",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、眼下当务之急的问题、是该如何逃{00}到安全圈",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602e90bef4def53e94fe7cdea62e7b4e997ea1202e7b6e898e7f0efbce8c200e7d7e7fcefb4e9fb0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3b6b",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "PLANT派来的追兵、此刻肯定正在这一带{00}四处搜寻我们",
   "zh_hex": "15eed4e024ea9ceed3eed6e985d9e7b4e8ddce02e7cae91fe93de867ef3bef29e7b987e93700eb52e903ed6defe28be7bb0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3ba9",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "再说、刚才那场战斗里受的损伤、也得找{00}个地方修理才行",
   "zh_hex": "15e80be7ed02e8bce836e7b7e876ef28e7ffef31e8c8e7b4ea28e8f902e7c0e80ae9d200e828ef63efb1e9b0e872e836efd60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3be2",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来、{00}眼下还是先避开追兵才是要紧事……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6d90200e90b89e7f7e7b6b8cae7fae8ddcee836e7b6ef2aeaeda909090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3bfb",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这附近、有没有能藏身的地方？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9eaf8efd802e7cbe7d8e7cbe7c6ed03e88de7b4ef63efb1050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3c2c",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在稍微远一点的地方、有一座废弃的殖民{00}地……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29ead5eb58e94cefb6e822e7b4ef63efb102e7cbefb6ebc4eae5e938e7b4e8a9ef3800ef6309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3c41",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就是孟德尔殖民地",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7b6ec5ee82ce7e1e8a9ef38ef630000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3c65",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那就先去那座孟德尔殖民地、抢修受损的{00}舰艇和MS",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c5ef8be7ebe7b7ebc4ec5ee82ce7e1e8a9ef38ef6302ebc8e9b0e8c8ea28e7b400e7d4eb6be7d3efa7ef9e0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3c83",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "之后、再摆脱追击的部队、脱离扎夫特的{00}势力圈……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cde7fe02e80beb8be9e5e8dde7cce7b4ef70e7c902e9e5e901e84be830e7cfe7b400e8fdefb0e9fb09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3ca2",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就这样办",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7b9e7dae8ea0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3cc9",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "说得对、只要能脱离扎夫特的势力圈……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7ede80ae7be02ef32ef2ae7c6e9e5e901e84be830e7cfe7b4e8fdefb0e9fb09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3ce1",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "便能和奥古、迪安娜回归军这些友军取得{00}联动",
   "zh_hex": "15e8fae7c6e7d3e82be84d02ea11e7fce7eaef52e947e7e0e7b9e8a4e960e7e0e987e80a00ef2eef300000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3cfa",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "先照那方针办",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8bea1ae7b7efb1ebf8e8ea0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3d20",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……原来如此",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8e4efcfe7f0e7ca0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3d27",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您是要我去追击叛徒拉克丝·克莱因、是{00}这个意思吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7b6ef2a8be7ebe8dde7ccef43eb02e7c2e7d5e8a304e7d5e846ef3302e7b600e7b9e828ef3ca6e7d0050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3d60",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他们身边、还跟着自由和正义两台机体",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7bbe88de89902e7f7e973e86dabe8a6e7d3ef3be8cee97dea16e7e4bc00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3d90",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是N干扰消除器吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6eed3e8d3ebc7e928e974e8c3e7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3db5",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在落入那帮自然人手里之前、无论如何都{00}要处理掉……明白吗",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e92ae891e7b7e910efb5e7efefb2ef66ef31e7cdef5102e7dce8dce7f0efbce84000ef2ae903e872e9d30909ef39e809e8020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3dee",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……全力以赴",
   "zh_hex": "150909efb4efb0e7f3eb1c0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3e4c",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵呵……要去追击拉克丝·克莱因吗",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3def3d0909ef2ae7ebe8dde7cce7c2e7d5e8a304e7d5e846ef33e802000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3e5d",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要紧追着大天使号、那OZ也必然会现{00}身……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2aeaede8dde86defa5e844e83fe83302e7b7ed1ceedae7c0e860e7efe7e2e82f00e88d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3e73",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这可是使用那把钥匙的绝佳机会",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7c4e7b6e83fefb3e7b7e81be78eef17e7b4e91cebb3e7e4e7e20000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3ea2",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "钥、钥匙……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e78e02e78eef170909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3ec7",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……你在啊",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b8ef29e7c30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3eed",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那个……您说的那把钥匙、是指……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e8280909e835e7ede7b4e7b7e81be78eef1702e7b6e8c009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3f18",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "没错……就是那把钥匙",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d8e8850909e7c5e7b6e7b7e81be78eef170000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3f22",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是用来打开那道门的钥匙",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6d8d9e7f5e7fae7b7e82ae90ce7b4e78eef1700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3f4b",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "钥匙、还有门……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e78eef1702e7f7e7cbe90c0909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3f78",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "用不了多久、也要请你来扮演一个角色了",
   "zh_hex": "15d8e7b5e7bae7e9e9db02e7c0ef2ae83ae7b8d9ec70ea2f87e828eb1ae89fe7ba0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3f90",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为了打开那道门……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e7bae7f5e7fae7b7e82ae90c09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3fb5",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "第七机动舰队、娜塔尔·巴基露露少佐…{00}…前来报到",
   "zh_hex": "15e940ec45e7e4ef30e7d4e7c902e7eae945e7e1ef4be85be829e858e858efacefba090009ef51efcfe913e7d70000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3feb",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哟、正等你呢",
   "zh_hex": "15eb2c02ef3be826e7b8e9070000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x4014",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请问您是？",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae997e835e7b6050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x403b",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这位是蓝色宇宙的理事、穆尔塔·阿兹拉{00}埃尔先生",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e834e7b6eaf1e89fe8bee8bfe7b4e872a902eb10e7e1e94504e7d2e856e7c200e96ae7e1b8b6000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x4052",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他将作为观察员、登上你所指挥的那艘舰",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce84aef2fe7c1eaf2ea8be84902e9a0ef4ce7b8e7fbe8c0e949e7b4e7b7eb18e7d40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x408b",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "观察员？还有、您说的那艘舰、是指……",
   "zh_hex": "15eaf2ea8be84905e7f7e7cb02e835e7ede7b4e7b7eb18e7d402e7b6e8c009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x40ba",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这是我军此番刚服役的新锐舰、主天使号",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7b6efcce7e0e7caee6de8bce9f1ed59e7b4ef8aed14e7d402e954e844e83fe8330000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x40d1",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们已决定、由你来担任这艘主天使号的{00}舰长",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbef3ae8abe86702e8a6e7b8efcfe9fde89ae7b9eb18e954e844e83fe833e7b400e7d4ef340000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x4108",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你、之前在大天使号上当过副长、对吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b802e7cdbaef29bee844e83fe833b2c4ef36ecb6ef3402e7bee7d005000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x411f",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我就是想请你把那份经验好好用上",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7c5e7b6e7e6e83ae7b8e81be7b7ea22e8b7ea99e7c7e7c7efb3ef4c0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x414c",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bd0909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x416e",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "去讨伐他们",
   "zh_hex": "15e7ebe9f7eb26e80ce7bb0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x417b",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "接下来啊、我们就是要去打那艘大天使号",
   "zh_hex": "15efceef4defcfe7c302efcce7bbe7c5e7b6ef2ae7ebe7f5e7b7eb18efa5e844e83fe8330000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x41aa",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x41d2",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿兹拉埃尔先生动身前往了宇宙……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e856e7c2e96ae7e1ef8bef8def30e88def51e911e7bae8bee8bf09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x41e3",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "还有、米利亚尔特、你也……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f7e7cb02e878e82ee7d6e7e1e7cf02e7b8e7c009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x41fc",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我的友人啊、看来你也已下定了决心",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce7b4e960efb2e7c302e7f6efcfe7b8e7c0ef3aef4de867e7bae8abe82d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x4212",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、我便……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02efcce8fa09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9fb2",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎、怎么会到此为止……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f202e7f2e7bde7e2e7d7e7cae7c1e86909090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9ff2",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "PLANT又有新部队出动了！",
   "zh_hex": "15eed4e024ea9ceed3eed6e8f1e7cbef8acce7c9afef30e7ba06000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa01d",
